HEADWORD: En bloc
<hw>En` bloc"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[F. Cf. <er>Block</er>,
<pos>n.</pos> ]</ety> <def>In a lump; as a whole; all together.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Movement of the ossicles <xex>en bloc</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Nature.</au></rj></p>

<p><q><qex>En bloc</qex> they are known as ⟦ldquo⟧the herd⟦rdquo⟧.</q>
